<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>钢材重量计算器</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#f4f7fb;
      --card:#ffffff;
      --text:#1f2937;
      --muted:#6b7280;
      --line:#dbe3ef;
      --blue:#2563eb;
      --blue-soft:#eaf2ff;
      --green:#16a34a;
      --green-soft:#ebf9f0;
      --orange:#d97706;
      --orange-soft:#fff5e6;
      --purple:#7c3aed;
      --purple-soft:#f3ecff;
      --red:#dc2626;
      --red-soft:#fff1f2;
      --shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      --radius:18px;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box;}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:"Microsoft YaHei","PingFang SC","Noto Sans SC",Arial,sans-serif;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#eef5ff 0%, #f8fbff 180px, var(--bg) 180px);
      color:var(--text);
    }

    .container{
      max-width:1280px;
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:24px 18px 40px;
    }

    .hero{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1849d6 0%,#2563eb 40%,#4f46e5 100%);
      color:#fff;
      border-radius:24px;
      padding:28px 28px 24px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      margin-bottom:20px;
    }

    .hero h1{
      margin:0 0 12px;
      font-size:30px;
      line-height:1.2;
    }

    .hero p{
      margin:0;
      opacity:0.95;
      line-height:1.7;
      font-size:15px;
      max-width:980px;
    }

    .tag-row{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
      margin-top:16px;
    }

    .tag{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      color:#fff;
      padding:8px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-size:13px;
    }

    .layout{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap:20px;
      align-items:start;
    }

    .panel{
      background:var(--card);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
      border:1px solid rgba(219,227,239,0.8);
    }

    .panel-head{
      padding:18px 20px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
      background:#fbfdff;
    }

    .panel-head h2{
      margin:0 0 8px;
      font-size:20px;
    }

    .panel-head p{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
      line-height:1.7;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .panel-body{
      padding:20px;
    }

    .card{
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:18px;
      margin-bottom:16px;
      background:#fff;
    }

    .card:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}

    .card.blue{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#ffffff 0%, var(--blue-soft) 100%);
      border-color:#cfe0ff;
    }
    .card.green{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#ffffff 0%, var(--green-soft) 100%);
      border-color:#cdeed9;
    }
    .card.orange{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#ffffff 0%, var(--orange-soft) 100%);
      border-color:#ffe1b7;
    }
    .card.purple{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#ffffff 0%, var(--purple-soft) 100%);
      border-color:#e2d3ff;
    }

    .card-title{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:10px;
      margin-bottom:14px;
    }

    .card-title h3{
      margin:0;
      font-size:16px;
    }

    .hint{
      font-size:12px;
      color:var(--muted);
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    .grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));
      gap:14px;
    }

    .grid-1{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .grid-3{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));}

    .field{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap:6px;
    }

    .field label{
      font-size:13px;
      color:#374151;
      font-weight:600;
    }

    .field input,
    .field select,
    .field textarea{
      width:100%;
      border:1px solid #cfd8e3;
      border-radius:12px;
      padding:12px 12px;
      font-size:14px;
      color:var(--text);
      background:#fff;
      outline:none;
      transition:all .18s ease;
    }

    .field input:focus,
    .field select:focus,
    .field textarea:focus{
      border-color:#7aa9ff;
      box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(37,99,235,.10);
    }

    .field small{
      color:var(--muted);
      line-height:1.5;
      font-size:12px;
    }

    .inline-note{
      margin-top:10px;
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-radius:12px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      border:1px dashed #cfd8e3;
      font-size:13px;
      color:#475569;
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    .actions{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:12px;
      margin-top:18px;
    }

    button{
      border:none;
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:12px 18px;
      font-size:14px;
      font-weight:700;
      cursor:pointer;
      transition:transform .12s ease, box-shadow .12s ease, opacity .12s ease;
    }

    button:hover{
      transform:translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn-primary{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#4f46e5);
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(37,99,235,0.22);
    }

    .btn-success{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#16a34a,#0f9f74);
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(22,163,74,0.18);
    }

    .btn-light{
      background:#eef2f7;
      color:#1f2937;
    }

    .btn-danger{
      background:#fff1f2;
      color:#b91c1c;
      border:1px solid #fecdd3;
    }

    .result-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));
      gap:14px;
      margin-bottom:14px;
    }

    .result-item{
      background:#fff;
      border:1px solid #cdeed9;
      border-radius:16px;
      padding:16px;
    }

    .result-item .label{
      color:#4b5563;
      font-size:13px;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .result-item .value{
      font-size:24px;
      font-weight:800;
      color:#0f172a;
      word-break:break-word;
    }

    .result-item .sub{
      margin-top:6px;
      color:#6b7280;
      font-size:12px;
    }

    .formula{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      border:1px dashed #cdeed9;
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:14px;
      line-height:1.7;
      color:#334155;
      font-size:13px;
    }

    .summary-bar{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));
      gap:12px;
      margin-bottom:16px;
    }

    .summary-box{
      background:#fff;
      border-radius:16px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      padding:16px;
    }

    .summary-box .label{
      color:#6b7280;
      font-size:13px;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .summary-box .value{
      font-size:24px;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .summary-box.blue-border{border-color:#cfe0ff;}
    .summary-box.green-border{border-color:#cdeed9;}
    .summary-box.orange-border{border-color:#ffe1b7;}

    .table-wrap{
      overflow:auto;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:16px;
      background:#fff;
    }

    table{
      width:100%;
      border-collapse:collapse;
      min-width:850px;
    }

    th, td{
      padding:12px 10px;
      border-bottom:1px solid #edf2f7;
      text-align:left;
      font-size:13px;
      vertical-align:top;
    }

    th{
      background:#f8fbff;
      color:#334155;
      font-weight:700;
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:1;
    }

    tbody tr:hover{
      background:#fafcff;
    }

    .empty{
      padding:22px;
      text-align:center;
      color:#6b7280;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .pill{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:6px;
      background:#eff6ff;
      color:#1d4ed8;
      border:1px solid #dbeafe;
      padding:6px 10px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .warn-list{
      margin:0;
      padding-left:18px;
      color:#475569;
      line-height:1.8;
      font-size:13px;
    }

    .footer-note{
      margin-top:18px;
      color:#6b7280;
      font-size:12px;
      line-height:1.7;
    }

    .delete-btn{
      padding:8px 10px;
      border-radius:10px;
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:700;
      background:#fff1f2;
      color:#b91c1c;
      border:1px solid #fecdd3;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px){
      .layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px){
      .grid,
      .grid-3,
      .result-grid,
      .summary-bar{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .hero h1{font-size:24px;}
      .panel-body, .panel-head, .hero{padding:18px;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>钢材重量计算器（HTML 单文件版）</h1>
      <p>
        适合现场快速核算理论重量与金额。支持圆钢、钢管、方管、矩形管、实心方钢、扁钢、钢板、花纹板、角钢、工字钢、槽钢、H 型钢、钢筋等常见钢材。
        圆钢/板材类按尺寸自动计算，型钢类可直接选常用规格并自动带出理论单位重，也支持手动修正。
      </p>
      <div class="tag-row">
        <span class="tag">默认密度：碳钢 7850 kg/m³</span>
        <span class="tag">支持塔卡单价</span>
        <span class="tag">支持加入清单汇总</span>
        <span class="tag">支持修改理论单位重</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="layout">
      <section class="panel">
        <div class="panel-head">
          <h2>输入与计算</h2>
          <p>先选择钢材类型，再输入尺寸、长度、数量、密度和单价，点击“立即计算”。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <div class="card blue">
            <div class="card-title">
              <h3>1. 钢材类型与规格</h3>
              <span class="pill">蓝色区域：规格与尺寸</span>
            </div>

            <div class="grid">
              <div class="field">
                <label for="steelType">钢材种类</label>
                <select id="steelType"></select>
                <small>选择不同钢材后，下面会自动切换对应输入项。</small>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label for="materialPreset">材料密度预设</label>
                <select id="materialPreset"></select>
                <small>可先选预设，再根据需要手动修改密度值。</small>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div id="dynamicForm" style="margin-top:16px;"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="card purple">
            <div class="card-title">
              <h3>2. 密度与单价</h3>
              <span class="pill" style="background:#f5f3ff;color:#6d28d9;border-color:#e9d5ff;">紫色区域：材料参数</span>
            </div>

            <div class="grid">
              <div class="field">
                <label for="density">材料密度（kg/m³）</label>
                <input id="density" type="number" step="1" min="1" value="7850" />
                <small>常用碳钢默认 7850；不锈钢、铝、铜等可切换预设后自动带出。</small>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label for="pricePerKg">单价（塔卡 / kg）</label>
                <input id="pricePerKg" type="number" step="0.01" min="0" value="0" />
                <small>输入钢材采购单价后，可自动算出总金额。</small>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <button class="btn-primary" id="calcBtn">立即计算</button>
            <button class="btn-success" id="addBtn">加入清单</button>
            <button class="btn-light" id="resetBtn">重置当前输入</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel">
        <div class="panel-head">
          <h2>结果与说明</h2>
          <p>这里会显示当前规格的单件重量、总重量、金额以及采用的计算方式。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <div class="card green">
            <div class="card-title">
              <h3>3. 当前计算结果</h3>
              <span class="pill" style="background:#f0fdf4;color:#15803d;border-color:#bbf7d0;">绿色区域：结果</span>
            </div>

            <div class="result-grid">
              <div class="result-item">
                <div class="label">单件/单根理论重量</div>
                <div class="value" id="singleWeight">0.000 kg</div>
                <div class="sub">按当前规格计算</div>
              </div>
              <div class="result-item">
                <div class="label">总理论重量</div>
                <div class="value" id="totalWeight">0.000 kg</div>
                <div class="sub">数量 × 单件重量</div>
              </div>
              <div class="result-item">
                <div class="label">总金额</div>
                <div class="value" id="totalPrice">0.00 Tk</div>
                <div class="sub">总重量 × 单价</div>
              </div>
              <div class="result-item">
                <div class="label">当前规格摘要</div>
                <div class="value" id="resultSpec" style="font-size:18px;">未计算</div>
                <div class="sub" id="resultMeta">等待输入</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="formula" id="formulaBox">
              选择钢材并输入数据后，这里会显示计算依据。
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card orange">
            <div class="card-title">
              <h3>4. 使用提示</h3>
              <span class="pill" style="background:#fff7ed;color:#c2410c;border-color:#fed7aa;">橙色区域：说明</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="warn-list">
              <li>本页面计算的是<strong>理论重量</strong>，实际过磅重量会受公差、材质、生产标准影响。</li>
              <li>角钢、工字钢、槽钢、H 型钢使用的是<strong>常用理论单位重</strong>，并允许你手动修改。</li>
              <li>花纹板默认按 <strong>基板重量 × 1.06</strong> 估算，你也可以自行修改系数。</li>
              <li>钢筋可直接输入直径、长度、数量，系统按常用理论公式自动换算。</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <section class="panel" style="margin-top:20px;">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <h2>采购清单汇总</h2>
        <p>每次计算完成后，可以点击“加入清单”，把多个规格累加汇总，方便采购和报价。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="summary-bar">
          <div class="summary-box blue-border">
            <div class="label">清单条目数</div>
            <div class="value" id="sumItems">0</div>
          </div>
          <div class="summary-box green-border">
            <div class="label">清单总重量</div>
            <div class="value" id="sumWeight">0.000 kg</div>
          </div>
          <div class="summary-box orange-border">
            <div class="label">清单总金额</div>
            <div class="value" id="sumAmount">0.00 Tk</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th style="width:52px;">#</th>
                <th>钢材类型</th>
                <th>规格摘要</th>
                <th>数量</th>
                <th>单件重量</th>
                <th>总重量</th>
                <th>单价</th>
                <th>金额</th>
                <th style="width:90px;">操作</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="listBody">
              <tr><td colspan="9" class="empty">暂无数据，先计算后点击“加入清单”。</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn-light" id="clearListBtn">清空清单</button>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-note">
          备注：如果你要接入自己公司的真实规格表，只需要把下面脚本里的 profileTables 数据替换成你的标准数据即可。
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script>
    const materialPresets = {
      carbonSteel: { label: "碳钢 / 普通钢", density: 7850 },
      stainless304: { label: "不锈钢 304", density: 7930 },
